data.description: Are you looking for a great location? Well your search has ended! This diamond in the rough is easily accessed and backs up to the National Forest.  It is believed to be a Nash design and the layout is perfect for the whole family! Three bedrooms are on the entry level and there is one more upstairs.  The open living area has high ceilings and access to the large deck.  Live The Tahoe Lifestyle!
